sep.gaia.resources.markeroption

Class MarkerResourceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.ResourceObservable<R>
      • sep.gaia.resources.DataResourceManager<MarkerResource>
        • sep.gaia.resources.markeroption.MarkerResourceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StateObserver

    public class MarkerResourceManager
extends DataResourceManager<MarkerResource>
    This class is to manage a list of all the MarkerResource generated by the user. Every MarkerResource in this list has the same icon loaded from the SymbolLoader.
    Author:
    Michael Mitterer
